| AvoidSilentServiceOnBoot.java:19:9:19:63 | startService(...) | BroadcastReceiver BootReceiver calls startService() from onReceive(). If this receiver listens for BOOT_COMPLETED, this silently starts a service at boot, draining battery. Consider using JobScheduler or WorkManager. |
| AvoidSilentServiceOnBoot.java:27:9:27:73 | startForegroundService(...) | BroadcastReceiver BootForegroundReceiver calls startService() from onReceive(). If this receiver listens for BOOT_COMPLETED, this silently starts a service at boot, draining battery. Consider using JobScheduler or WorkManager. |
